Ronne Troup https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ronne_Troup 0 Ronne Troup (born June 10, 1945 in Bryn Mawr, Pennsylvania) is an American actress and educator best known for her 1970–72 role as "Polly Williams Douglas" on the long-running sitcom My Three Sons.
